show.description: A weak laborer, Yash, mysteriously gains superhuman strength. As he impresses many, he's betrayed by his girlfriend Tanya, who plots to steal his family’s secret formula. When his mentor is attacked, Yash prepares to fight back and reclaim his dignity.
